The Cybrats seemed to have the Autobots pinned between them when a sudden
Photon blast flew through the smoke striking Branding knocking her off her
feet and disabling one of her flamethrowers. She rolled around a corner to
use the building as cover while she assessed her damage. "WE Better make
this quick" she shouted over her comm to the other Cybrats." Reinforcements
are arriving quickly." she was ecstatic at this point, the femm always knew
that sooner or later they'd hit the wrong target, and this was quickly
becomming that time.

Arty's equilibreum was sent into a state of confusion as Swoops missles took
effect (I'm thinking that A-G missles would have that effect instead of
causing impact damage.) the tank transformed, his twin cannons taking thier
positions on his shoulders. He fired both barrels at Pacifix hoping to clear
a way for thier escape. Flames from Slag engulfed him from behind making him
greatfull for his thick hide, the temperature was riseing and his missles
were useless, if he were to arm one in that temperature it would explode
before he could launch it.

> --- Pacifix / Crossroads / Swoop ---
>
> Pacifix, after driving for a while, arrives at the the entrance. He
> hears noise, and transforms quickly, and enters the hole. When he
> gets to the bottom, and views the carnage below. "STOP," he yells
> into the battle, as he comes out of the entrance in barricade mode,
> prepared to defend.
>
> Crossroads leaps up, and starts running towards the small battle,
> his mind having already decided that the Autobots have military
> tactical advantage in numbers and skill over the apparent enemies.
> He notes that the smoke grenade will be a nuisance. His photon
> cannons hum and two photon blasts head to one of the bots
> (Brandings).
>
> Swoop follows Crossroads. he transforms into Pterodactyl mode,
> and heads towards the enemy bots. He launches four A-G missiles
> at a different bot (Arty). "Swoop will help Grimlock!" he yells to
> Grimlock.
